  <h1>Public Work</h1>
  <p>I share my research in public forums and collaborative projects across performance, media, and community venues. Recent venues include UCLA and UNC Greensboro; public-facing events range from opera talkbacks to K&ndash;12 educator programs. Below are selected appearances and creative Projects, with links to recordings or documentation when available.</p>

